        </div>
        <div class="reveal">
            <div class="section-tag">Who Needs This</div>
            <h2 class="art-h2">Who Needs Lead Management?</h2>
            <p class="art-p">If your business generates leads, you need structured lead management.</p>
            <div class="art-grid-2">
                <div class="art-mini-card">Sales teams</div>
                <div class="art-mini-card">IT companies</div>
